meaning that sailing westward,

00:15:19.940 --> 00:15:21.450
you could get to the East.

00:15:21.450 --> 00:15:25.230
And that's what Columbus
really was aware of.

00:15:25.230 --> 00:15:32.130
And Columbus was also aware that
the globe, the earth was rounded,

00:15:32.130 --> 00:15:37.910
especially after this
globe was made in 1492.

00:15:37.910 --> 00:15:43.000
So, Columbus made several attempts
to convince kings in Portugal

00:15:43.000 --> 00:15:48.230
and Spain for his trip, for his
so-called enterprise of the Indies.

00:15:48.230 --> 00:15:50.750
Remember that Columbus
died believing

00:15:50.750 --> 00:15:52.190
