00:35:48.800 --> 00:35:50.150
They came the other way.

00:35:50.150 --> 00:35:54.010
They came from the east,
so they, they took over.

00:35:54.010 --> 00:35:59.000
And after that, they
exchanged Havana,

00:35:59.000 --> 00:36:01.110
